# ClaudeChan - Environment Variables
# ====================================

# OpenRouter API Key (required for real AI responses)
# --------------------------------------------------
# 1. Go to https://openrouter.ai/keys
# 2. Sign up or log in
# 3. Create a new API key
# 4. Copy the key and paste below
#
# The API uses gpt-4o-mini by default (~$0.15/1M tokens input)
# You can add credits at https://openrouter.ai/account
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# Your site URL (for OpenRouter attribution)
# Used in API headers for rate limiting and tracking
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-site.vercel.app

# ====================================
# DEMO MODE (No API Key Required)
# ====================================
# Both apps work without an API key:
# - Duality Oracle: Shows pre-written philosophical debates
# - Survival Game: Shows pre-written game events
#
# To enable real AI:
# 1. Get an OpenRouter API key above
# 2. Add it to Vercel Environment Variables:
#    - Go to your Vercel project dashboard
#    - Settings -> Environment Variables
#    - Add OPENROUTER_API_KEY with your key
# 3. Redeploy the project
